abstract: How this watery fluid became an essential skin care product.
snippet: How this watery fluid became an essential skin care product.
lead_paragraph: It has been called “miracle water,” but an essence — the beauty product that’s considered an integral step in Korean and Japanese skin-care routines — is no water.

abstract: From an English country inn to a Caribbean beach resort, places our correspondents love to stay (you will like them too).

lead_paragraph: What makes a hotel your favorite? The favorite? Every traveler has a different criteria: some love grand properties with opulent décor, while others prefer small places with a personal touch. The service, the food, the rooms and the setting usually figure in too.

abstract: Two end-of-the-world films worth comparing and contrasting: “How It Ends,” on Netflix, and the 1970 movie “No Blade of Grass,” on Amazon Prime.
snippet: Two end-of-the-world films worth comparing and contrasting: “How It Ends,” on Netflix, and the 1970 movie “No Blade of Grass,” on Amazon Prime.
lead_paragraph: There’s nothing like a good end-of-the-world-as-we-know-it movie to get you through the dog days. I recall whiling away an August afternoon at my local single-screen theater with “The Omega Man” back in 1971, the summer I turned 12. No wonder I was such a morbid kid, growing up watching Charlton Heston screen “Woodstock” for his movie-palace audience of one in between fighting off zombielike hordes led by Anthony Zerbe.

abstract: The N.R.A.’s renewed battle with the governor has given him ready-made talking points in his campaign for re-election in New York.
snippet: The N.R.A.’s renewed battle with the governor has given him ready-made talking points in his campaign for re-election in New York.
lead_paragraph: When the National Rifle Association brought its Carry Guard insurance program to New York in April of last year, it marketed it as the solution to a pressing concern among its loyal followers, a protection against legal fees that could arise from firing a weapon in self-defense.

abstract: An increasingly vocal group of Chinese-Americans who were once politically dormant has been galvanized by the fight over race-based school admissions.
snippet: An increasingly vocal group of Chinese-Americans who were once politically dormant has been galvanized by the fight over race-based school admissions.
lead_paragraph: IRVINE, Calif. — George Li grew up in a Chinese society that he felt did not offer a fair shake. The government of Mao Zedong deemed his family capitalists and imprisoned his father.

abstract: Shahidul Alam, Bangladesh’s best-known photojournalist, was arrested after posting Facebook video in which he appeared to criticize the government’s handling of recent student-led protests.
snippet: Shahidul Alam, Bangladesh’s best-known photojournalist, was arrested after posting Facebook video in which he appeared to criticize the government’s handling of recent student-led protests.
lead_paragraph: The last time the acclaimed Bangladeshi photographer Shahidul Alam had a major run-in with the police, it was for a 2010 project documenting official torture and death squads, which led the Dhaka police to besiege and shut down his gallery and provoked national protests on his behalf.
